column6: More shorter-length stories featuring the Amazing Spider-Man and members of his all-star supporting cast, including "MAKING CONTRIBUTIONS", in which Mary Jane finds out how a person without her husband's superhero abilities can help make a difference!
column8: | penciller:Paul Azaceta | penciller:Rick Mays | writer:Adam Higgs | writer:J.t. Krul | penciller (cover):Andy Kubert
